title: Robert Ludlum (Bourne 05) - The Bourne Betrayal
description:
Jason Bourne takes a mission to rescue his only friend in the CIA, Martin 
Lindros, who disappeared in Africa while tracking shipments of yellowcake 
uranium. Once safely back in America, Lindros persuades Bourne to help 
track the money trail of terrorists buying the nuclear material in Odessa.--

But once there, Bourne is hampered by confusing flashbacks of unfamiliar 
places and events and he wonders: Is someone brainwashing him in order 
to throw him off the trail? Worse, is the man he saved in Africa really 
Martin Lindros? Now, Bourne is alone gathering evidence while trying 
to stay one step ahead of the terrorists who won't let anyone stand 
in their way of destroying the U.S
